  "raw_meta_yaml": "context:\n  version: 3.3.0\n\npackage:\n  name: libpninexus\n  version: ${{ version }}\n\nsource:\n  url: https://github.com/pni-libraries/libpninexus/archive/refs/tags/v${{ version }}.tar.gz\n  sha256: 54b902829ba7a01f889976d72e29c782a07675ae664896da1149c7c9a3f921b0\n  patches:\n    - add-template-argument-list.patch\n\nbuild:\n  number: 1\n  script:\n    - if: win\n      then:\n        - set CL=/DH5_BUILT_AS_DYNAMIC_LIB=1 %CL%\n        - cmake -B build -G Ninja  %CMAKE_ARGS%  -DHDF5_FIND_DEBUG=ON  -DHDF5_USE_STATIC_LIBRARIES=OFF -DPNINEXUS_CONAN=DISABLE\n      else: cmake -B build  ${CMAKE_ARGS}  -DPNINEXUS_CONAN=DISABLE\n    - cmake --build build  --target all\n    - cmake --install build\n    - cmake --build build  --target check\n\nrequirements:\n  build:\n    - ${{ compiler('cxx') }}\n    - ${{ stdlib('c') }}\n    - cmake\n    - ninja\n    - doxygen\n    - graphviz\n    - ghostscript\n    - sphinx\n    - breathe\n    - pygments\n    - if: not win\n      then:\n        - make\n        - cppunit\n  host:\n    - hdf5\n    - h5cpp\n    - boost-cpp\n    - zlib\n  run_exports:\n    - ${{ pin_subpackage(\"libpninexus\", upper_bound=\"x.x\") }}\n\ntests:\n  - package_contents:\n      include:\n        - pni/nexus/file.hpp\n        - pni/nexus/xml/create.hpp\n        - pni/nexus/path/path.hpp\n        - pni/parsers/parser.hpp\n        - pni/parsers.hpp\n      lib:\n        - pninexus\n\nabout:\n  homepage: https://github.com/pni-libraries/libpninexus\n  license: GPL-2.0-only\n  license_file: COPYING\n  summary: C++ NeXus library\n  description: |\n    libpninexus is C++ library to create NeXus files.\n    It provides NeXus tree-structure builder basedon XML (NXDL-like) input,\n    NeXus path parsers and other algorithms to access NeXus files.\n  documentation: https://pni-libraries.github.io/libpninexus\n  repository: https://github.com/pni-libraries/libpninexus\n\nextra:\n  recipe-maintainers:\n    - jkotan\n    - yuelongyu\n",
